<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 04:08:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴基斯坦将关闭“禁毒部办公室”，以消除国家财政不必要的负担</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-to-close-narcotics-control-ministry-office-to-eliminate-unnecessary-burden-on-national-exchequer/articleshow/108480548.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108480548.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据 ARY News 报道，巴基斯坦内政部长穆赫辛·纳克维 (Mohsin Naqvi) 宣布关闭禁毒部办公室，并将其业务并入内政部，理由是“消除国家财政不必要的负担”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-to-close-narcotics-control-ministry-office-to-eliminate-unnecessary-burden-on-national-exchequer/articleshow/108480548.cms</guid></item><item><title>丹麦计划首次将征兵范围扩大到女性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/denmark-plans-to-expand-military-draft-to-women-for-the-first-time-and-extend-service-terms/articleshow/108480220.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108480220.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;丹麦旨在通过扩大女性征兵范围和延长服役期限来实现军队中的性别平等。这一决定受到欧洲安全局势以及瑞典和挪威经验的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/denmark-plans-to-expand-military-draft-to-women-for-the-first-time-and-extend-service-terms/articleshow/108480220.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗人利用假期跳舞、跳过火堆来藐视规则</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dancing-and-jumping-over-fire-iranians-use-holiday-to-defy-rules/articleshow/108479977.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108479977.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗人在火节上反抗教权政府，高呼自由口号。数千人聚集在德黑兰，造成交通堵塞。年轻人要求变革，想要推翻伊斯兰共和国。 2022 年，由妇女和女孩领导的全国性起义。据报告，爆炸物和烟花处理不安全造成人员伤亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dancing-and-jumping-over-fire-iranians-use-holiday-to-defy-rules/articleshow/108479977.cms</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，特朗普和拜登在这个关键摇摆州展开了激烈的斗争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-and-biden-in-close-fight-in-this-key-swing-state-poll/articleshow/108479645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108479645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;宾夕法尼亚州即将迎来另一场势均力敌的选举竞争。特朗普在登记选民中领先拜登，但不同的选民群体显示出不同的支持率。特朗普在某些人群中找到了强有力的支持。 MAGA 运动的影响力影响着特朗普的支持率。宾夕法尼亚州的政治格局仍然不稳定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-and-biden-in-close-fight-in-this-key-swing-state-poll/articleshow/108479645.cms</guid></item><item><title>致命事故后美国恢复在日本的鱼鹰飞行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/us-resumes-osprey-flights-in-japan-after-deadly-crash/articleshow/108479890.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108479890.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名当地官员表示，美国军方周四恢复了在日本的“鱼鹰”飞行，结束了在最近发生的一系列致命坠机事件后，倾转旋翼机停飞三个月的情况。 11月底，一架美国鱼鹰在日本附近坠毁，机上八人全部遇难，并促使美国在下个月决定在全球范围内停飞飞机。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/us-resumes-osprey-flights-in-japan-after-deadly-crash/articleshow/108479890.cms</guid></item><item><title>特鲁多政府批准的新“奥威尔式”法律可能会终身监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/no-free-speech-new-orwellian-law-endorsed-by-trudeau-govt-could-imprison-people-for-life/articleshow/108479688.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108479688.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 《加拿大网络危害法案》（Bill C-63）面临过度扩张的批评，主张对种族灭绝罪判处无期徒刑。它与《少数派报告》进行了比较。玛格丽特·阿特伍德称之为奥威尔式的。斯蒂芬摩尔批评它背离了民主规范。人们仍然对言论自由保护和煽动仇恨的惩罚感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:18:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/no-free-speech-new-orwellian-law-endorsed-by-trudeau-govt-could-imprison-people-for-life/articleshow/108479688.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国在针对犹太人和穆斯林的仇恨犯罪增加之际公布极端主义定义</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-unveils-new-extremism-definition-amid-rise-in-hate-crimes-against-jews-muslims/articleshow/108477431.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108477431.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国政府周四推出了极端主义的新定义，以应对哈马斯袭击以色列后针对犹太人和穆斯林的仇恨犯罪激增。英国首相里希·苏纳克本月早些时候警告称，“极端主义数量惊人增加”。破坏和犯罪”，使该国面临陷入“暴民统治”的风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 00:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-unveils-new-extremism-definition-amid-rise-in-hate-crimes-against-jews-muslims/articleshow/108477431.cms</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/what-happens-next-with-tiktok/articleshow/108474101.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108474101.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 00:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/what-happens-next-with-tiktok/articleshow/108474101.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登和特朗普准备参加马拉松式的白宫竞选</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-and-trump-gird-for-marathon-white-house-race/articleshow/108477216.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108477216.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;距离美国总统大选还有八个月，竞选活动从两党提名之争转向了阵地战，这有望成为人们记忆中时间最长、最残酷的正面对决之一。美国总统乔·拜登和他的前任唐纳德·特朗普——历史上最年长的两位提名人——本周刚刚结束初选，这场初选给两人都留下了战斗的伤痕，引发了人们对他们判断力和精神敏锐度的质疑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 00:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-and-trump-gird-for-marathon-white-house-race/articleshow/108477216.cms</guid></item><item><title>从莫斯科到孟买：俄罗斯贸易重心向南</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/from-moscow-to-mumbai-russia-pivots-south-for-trade/articleshow/108474264.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108474264.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于贸易限制，俄罗斯正在远离欧洲市场，与中国和印度建立联系。南北运输走廊铁路项目旨在促进与孟买和波斯湾国家的贸易。这条南线现已成为俄罗斯政策制定者关注的焦点，因为他们试图为其永久远离西方的计划建设基础设施。这项努力面临挑战，包括融资问题、对俄罗斯新合作伙伴可靠性的怀疑，以及西方针对与俄罗斯进行贸易的国家实施制裁的威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:38:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/from-moscow-to-mumbai-russia-pivots-south-for-trade/articleshow/108474264.cms</guid></item><item><title>三军情报局阴谋：阿克萨达姆袭击事件的难以捉摸的主谋古里出现在视频中，呼吁对印度发动战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/isi-plot-ghori-elusive-mastermind-of-akshardham-attack-appears-in-video-calls-for-war-against-india/articleshow/108474267.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108474267.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; ISI 发布了 2002 年古吉拉特邦甘地纳加尔阿克萨达姆神庙袭击事件的策划者法哈图拉·古里 (Farhatullah Ghori) 的视频，呼吁对印度发动战争。 Ghori 与多起恐怖袭击、在线激进运动有关，并使用 Facebook 进行恐怖主义活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/isi-plot-ghori-elusive-mastermind-of-akshardham-attack-appears-in-video-calls-for-war-against-india/articleshow/108474267.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度学生在美国摩托艇相撞后死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/indian-student-dies-in-us-after-jet-ski-collision/articleshow/108474269.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108474269.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/indian-student-dies-in-us-after-jet-ski-collision/articleshow/108474269.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的救济：选举案件中的 6 项指控被撤销</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/relief-for-trump-6-charges-in-election-case-nixed/articleshow/108474211.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108474211.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:36:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/relief-for-trump-6-charges-in-election-case-nixed/articleshow/108474211.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普再次对阵拜登，美国大选68年来首次重赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/its-trump-vs-biden-again-first-us-election-rematch-in-68-years/articleshow/108474111.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108474111.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔·拜登和唐纳德·特朗普获得了各自政党的总统提名，为 11 月份的大选重赛奠定了基础。拜登在民主党初选中面临的反对微乎其微，而特朗普则在爱荷华州获胜，清除了共和党主要竞争对手的竞争。拜登在民主党初选中只面临象征性的反对，这对于现任总统来说是典型的情况，而特朗普几个月来一直是民主党的主要领先者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/its-trump-vs-biden-again-first-us-election-rematch-in-68-years/articleshow/108474111.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京警告西方：如果主权受到威胁，俄罗斯准备发动核战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/putin-warns-again-that-russia-is-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapons-if-its-sovereignty-is-threatened/articleshow/108473623.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108473623.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;自 2022 年 2 月 24 日对乌克兰发动全面入侵以来，这位俄罗斯领导人多次表示他准备使用核武器。最近的此类威胁出现在他上个月的国情咨文中，当时他发表了讲话。西方警告称，加深参与乌克兰战事将面临爆发核战争的风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:26:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/putin-warns-again-that-russia-is-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapons-if-its-sovereignty-is-threatened/articleshow/108473623.cms</guid></item><item><title>众议院通过法案，迫使中国所有者出售 TikTok 或禁止该应用程序</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/house-passes-bill-to-force-tiktok-sale-from-chinese-owner-or-ban-the-app/articleshow/108473599.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108473599.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/house-passes-bill-to-force-tiktok-sale-from-chinese-owner-or-ban-the-app/articleshow/108473599.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京再次警告：“如果……俄罗斯准备使用核武器”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapon-if-putin-warns-again/articleshow/108471757.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108471757.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京重申准备使用核武器来保护主权。他强调需要与北约盟国和乌克兰进行认真讨论。普京提到了扰乱俄罗斯总统选举的行为，并谴责乌克兰在俄罗斯境内发动的袭击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapon-if-putin-warns-again/articleshow/108471757.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过禁止 TikTok 法案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-house-passes-bill-to-ban-tiktok/articleshow/108470610.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108470610.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:47:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-house-passes-bill-to-ban-tiktok/articleshow/108470610.cms</guid></item><item><title>连续数周的大雪和降雨造成至少 60 名阿富汗人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/at-least-60-afghans-killed-by-weeks-of-intense-snow-rain/articleshow/108467889.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108467889.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据阿富汗灾害部称，过去三周，阿富汗的大雨和大雪已夺去了至少60人的生命。尽管冬季干燥，但每年的这个时候通常会带来危险的天气，例如洪水，给社区造成严重破坏。贾南·萨耶克说：“不幸的是，由于雨雪天气，我们失去了60名同胞，23人受伤。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/at-least-60-afghans-killed-by-weeks-of-intense-snow-rain/articleshow/108467889.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国考虑向自愿移居卢旺达的移民支付费用</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-mulls-plan-to-pay-migrants-to-move-to-rwanda-voluntarily/articleshow/108465234.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108465234.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国政府周三表示，正在考虑一项计划，将被拒绝的寻求庇护者自愿送往卢旺达，据报道，英国政府将向他们支付高达 3,000 英镑（3,800 美元）的费用。该计划是现有自愿遣返安排的延伸，出台之际，部长们正在努力启动单独的有争议的提案，将其他移民驱逐到这个东非国家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:01:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-mulls-plan-to-pay-migrants-to-move-to-rwanda-voluntarily/articleshow/108465234.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>